The gandhaḥ— 
 

12
00:00:35,425 --> 00:00:37,123
the original fragrance 
of the Earth,

13
00:00:37,123 --> 00:00:44,903
All these varieties of aroma …
He’s raso vai saḥ, it’s Kṛṣṇa.

14
00:00:46,259 --> 00:00:47,719
These things 
should not be seen 
 

15
00:00:47,719 --> 00:00:52,633
or appreciated separately,
divorсed of Kṛṣṇa conception,
 

16
00:00:53,223 --> 00:00:54,933
